xojdei69/Screenshot_2017-12-28-10-57-23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2F4xojdei69%2FScreenshot_2017-12-28-10-57-23.png&h=2929b634&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>由此可見，肥鳩大隻哩隻食屎狗被本癲狗教化以後，有時都幾老實</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}